data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem. Situated on a generous lot, this property offers comfort, space, and versatility to meet all your needs. Step inside this welcoming abode, where you'll find an open floor plan that's perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. Whether you're a DIY enthusiast, an artist, or in need of extra storage space, the 24x32 metal shop with electricity is a versatile bonus feature of this property.
